(57, 15, 'en', '', '', '', '<p class=\"QN2lPu\" style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, 文泉驛正黑, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'儷黑 Pro\', \'LiHei Pro\', \'Heiti TC\', 微軟正黑體, \'Microsoft JhengHei UI\', \'Microsoft JhengHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">B&agrave;n l&agrave;m việc, b&agrave;n gaming chữ K,U,Z gi&aacute; xưởng k&iacute;ch thước 1,2m&amp;1m ch&acirc;n sắt 2x4cm sơn tĩnh điện chắc chắn lắp r&aacute;p dễ d&agrave;ng</p>\r\n<p class=\"QN2lPu\" style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, 文泉驛正黑, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'儷黑 Pro\', \'LiHei Pro\', \'Heiti TC\', 微軟正黑體, \'Microsoft JhengHei UI\', \'Microsoft JhengHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">✅ B&agrave;n ch&acirc;n K uốn Cong ( B&agrave;n K cong)</p>\r\n<p class=\"QN2lPu\" style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, 文泉驛正黑, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'儷黑 Pro\', \'LiHei Pro\', \'Heiti TC\', 微軟正黑體, \'Microsoft JhengHei UI\', \'Microsoft JhengHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">M&agrave;u sắc sản phẩm: Đen/trắng</p>\r\n<p class=\"QN2lPu\" style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, 文泉驛正黑, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'儷黑 Pro\', \'LiHei Pro\', \'Heiti TC\', 微軟正黑體, \'Microsoft JhengHei UI\', \'Microsoft JhengHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff;\">K&iacute;ch thước: DxRxC (120x60x75cm)</p>\r\n<p class=\"QN2lPu\" style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, 文泉驛正黑, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'儷黑 Pro\', \'LiHei Pro\'